00107         public string NextString(int Length, string AllowedCharacters,int NumberOfNonAlphaNumericsAllowed)
00108         {
00109             if (Length < 1)
00110                 return "";
00111             StringBuilder TempBuilder = new StringBuilder();
00112             Regex Comparer = new Regex(AllowedCharacters);
00113             Regex AlphaNumbericComparer=new Regex("[0-9a-zA-z]");
00114             int Counter = 0;
00115             while (TempBuilder.Length < Length)
00116             {
00117                 string TempValue = new string(Convert.ToChar(Convert.ToInt32(System.Math.Floor(94 * NextDouble() + 32))), 1);
00118                 if (Comparer.IsMatch(TempValue))
00119                 {
00120                     if (!AlphaNumbericComparer.IsMatch(TempValue) && NumberOfNonAlphaNumericsAllowed > Counter)
00121                     {
00122                         TempBuilder.Append(TempValue);
00123                         ++Counter;
00124                     }
00125                     else if (AlphaNumbericComparer.IsMatch(TempValue))
00126                     {
00127                         TempBuilder.Append(TempValue);
00128                     }
00129                 }
00130             }
00131             return TempBuilder.ToString();
00132         }

00139         public string NextLoremIpsum(int NumberOfWords)
00140         {
00141             StringBuilder Builder = new StringBuilder();
00142             Builder.Append(StringHelper.ToFirstCharacterUpperCase(Words[Next(Words.Length)]));
00143             for (int x = 1; x < NumberOfWords; ++x)
00144             {
00145                 Builder.Append(" " + Words[Next(Words.Length)]);
00146             }
00147             Builder.Append(".");
00148             return Builder.ToString();

00160         public string NextLoremIpsum(int NumberOfParagraphs, int NumberOfSentences, int MinSentenceLength, int MaxSentenceLength, bool HTMLFormatting)
00161         {
00162             StringBuilder Builder = new StringBuilder();
00163             if (HTMLFormatting)
00164                 Builder.Append("<p>");
00165             Builder.Append("Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. ");
00166             for (int y = 0; y < NumberOfSentences; ++y)
00167             {
00168                 Builder.Append(NextLoremIpsum(Next(MinSentenceLength, MaxSentenceLength)) + " ");
00169             }
00170             if (HTMLFormatting)
00171                 Builder.Append("</p>");
00172             for (int x = 1; x < NumberOfParagraphs; ++x)
00173             {
00174                 if (HTMLFormatting)
00175                     Builder.Append("<p>");
00176                 for (int y = 0; y < NumberOfSentences; ++y)
00177                 {
00178                     Builder.Append(NextLoremIpsum(Next(MinSentenceLength, MaxSentenceLength)) + " ");
00179                 }
00180                 if (HTMLFormatting)
00181                     Builder.Append("</p>");
00182                 else
00183                     Builder.Append(System.Environment.NewLine + System.Environment.NewLine);
00184             }
00185             return Builder.ToString();
00186         }

00218         {
00219             Array Values = Enum.GetValues(typeof(T));
